- provide(:title, 'Dataset')
- provide(:active, doc_datasets_path)

= content_for :header do
  = stylesheet_pack_tag 'static/common', media: :all

%main
  .container
    %h1.title
      TogoVar datasets

    %h2
      Human genome reference sequence
    %ul
      %li
        = link_to 'GRCh37.p13 (06/28/2013)', 'https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/grc/human/data?asm=GRCh37.p13', target: '_blank'

    %h2
      Variant datasets derived from individual genome data in Japanese Genotype­-phenotype Archive (JGA)
    %table.table.table-bordered.table-sm
      %thead.text-center
        %tr
          %th Dataset name
          %th Version/Last update
          %th Sample size
          %th Number of detected variants
          %th Number of variants after the exclusion
          %th Author
      %tbody
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'JGA-NGS', doc_datasets_jga_ngs_path
          %td 06/01/2018
          %td.text-right 125
          %td.text-right 13,338,968
          %td.text-right 4,679,025
          %td NBDC
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'JGA-SNP', doc_datasets_jga_snp_path
          %td 06/01/2018
          %td.text-right 183,884
          %td.text-right 1,966,919
          %td.text-right 1,249,724
          %td NBDC

    %em
      Note that variants with 5 alternative alleles or less were excluded from JGA-NGS and JGA-SNP datasets.

    %h2
      Variant datasets generated by third parties
    %table.table.table-bordered.table-sm
      %thead.text-center
        %tr
          %th Dataset name
          %th Version/Last update
          %th Sample size
          %th Number of variants
          %th Number of variant sites
          %th Author
      %tbody
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'ClinVar', 'ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/clinvar/', target: '_blank'
          %td 02/01/2017
          %td.text-center —
          %td.text-right 198,707
          %td.text-center —
          %td NCBI
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'Exome Aggregation Consortium (ExAC)', 'http://exac.broadinstitute.org/downloads', target: '_blank'
          %td Release 1 (02/27/2017)
          %td.text-right 60,706
          %td.text-right 10,195,872
          %td.text-right 9,362,319
          %td Broad Institute
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'Human Genetic Variation Database (HGVD)', 'http://www.hgvd.genome.med.kyoto-u.ac.jp/download.html', target: '_blank'
          %td Version 2.30 (08/02/2017)
          %td.text-right 1,208
          %td.text-right 554,461
          %td.text-right 501,556
          %td Kyoto University
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'Integrative Japanese Genome Variation Database (iJGVD)', 'https://ijgvd.megabank.tohoku.ac.jp/download_3.5kjpn/', target: '_blank'
          %td 3.5KJPN (09/28/2017)
          %td.text-right 3,554
          %td.text-center —
          %td.text-right 7,931,579
          %td Tohoku Medical Megabank Organization

    %em
      Note that of iJGVD 3.5KJPN variants, TogoVar contains only those accessible without DTA (i.e.  their frequencies
      are 1% or more). See #{link_to 'Data release', 'https://ijgvd.megabank.tohoku.ac.jp/', target: '_blank'} for details.

    %h2
      Datasets other than those for variants
    %table.table.table-bordered.table-sm
      %thead.text-center
        %tr
          %th Dataset name
          %th Version/Last update
          %th Description
          %th Author
      %tbody
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'Colil', 'ftp://ftp.dbcls.jp/colil', target: '_blank'
          %td 01/29/2018
          %td Information on citation relationships in life sciences literature
          %td DBCLS
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'PubTator', 'ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/lu/PubTator/', target: '_blank'
          %td 04/23/2018
          %td Information on papers in which the names of variants appear
          %td NCBI
        %tr
          %td= link_to 'TogoGenome', 'http://togogenome.org/', target: '_blank'
          %td hg19+UniProt_201804
          %td Various information on genomes
          %td DBCLS
